50|$|Domestic fryers {{often include}} a <b>safety</b> <b>cut-out</b> {{in case of}} overheating, for example if not enough oil is used or the fryer is {{switched}} on whilst empty. A reset button is included on most of these fryers to reset the safety device once the unit has cooled down; if a reset button is not included the fryer may need repairing if the safety device activates.|$|E

